cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.HC 

The paper deals with video action recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The experiments involve deep learning models, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The dataset and evaluation metrics are specific to video analysis (cs.MM), and the paper also discusses the importance of body language and human perception (cs.HC).
